bincimap needs to be started from inetd(8). Add the following line
to its configuration file (/etc/inetd.conf):

 imap stream tcp nowait root ${PREFIX}/bin/bincimap-up bincimap-up -c ${PREFIX}/etc/bincimap.conf -- ${PREFIX}/bin/checkpassword ${PREFIX}/bin/bincimapd Maildir

For sample configuration for other tcpwrappers look in
${PREFIX}/share/examples/bincimap.
===========================================================================
